10-Point EU AI Act Compliance Checklist
========================================

✅ Article 50 (Nov 2, 2026): Watermarking & deepfake disclosure ready?
✅ Article 53: High-risk AI system requirements documented?
✅ Article 16: Provider obligations & compliance mapped?
✅ NIST AI RMF: Risk management framework implemented?
✅ GDPR: AI data processing compliant?
✅ Bias Detection: Audit completed in last 90 days?
✅ Security: Prompt injection defenses tested?
✅ Incident Response: Plan documented & tested?
✅ Documentation: Technical documentation complete?
✅ Audit Trail: Immutable logs for all AI decisions?

